name: Day 2 of Quarantine: Fear
description:
Have you ever felt like you know nothing? 
Have you ever felt like nothing ever going to last, even if it was going well?
Have you ever just... felt scared, so scared of everything?

During day 2 of my quarantine, a lot of things added up. Being alone made me overthink pessimistically. I felt horrible when all the solutions you add up end up in the worst possible way. I was so afraid things were going to change in a bad way, even though it did not happen yet, even though there was so sign of it, and even though I knew it was only because of me overthinking. It was an unending loop of negative thoughts, round and round in a maze that I could not find a way out.
